## Phase 3 Enhancements - User Experience Improvements

### Copy-to-Clipboard Functionality

#### Implementation Strategy
- **Modern Clipboard API** with fallback for older browsers
- **Visual feedback** with button state changes (ðŸ“‹ â†’ âœ… Copied!)
- **Error handling** for clipboard permission issues
- **Cross-browser compatibility** using document.execCommand fallback

#### JavaScript Implementation
```javascript
async function copyToClipboard(text) {
    try {
        await navigator.clipboard.writeText(text);
        return true;
    } catch (err) {
        // Fallback for older browsers
        const textArea = document.createElement('textarea');
        textArea.value = text;
        textArea.style.position = 'fixed';
        textArea.style.left = '-999999px';
        document.body.appendChild(textArea);
        textArea.focus();
        textArea.select();
        
        try {
            document.execCommand('copy');
            document.body.removeChild(textArea);
            return true;
        } catch (err) {
            document.body.removeChild(textArea);
            return false;
        }
    }
}
```

